train.description: basic drive activities (e.g., drive; accelerate; decelerate; reverse; etc.)

correlated_signal_attack.description: start from driving; accelerate; start injecting; car rolls to stop; stop injecting; accelerate

fuzzing_attack.description: start from driving; accelerate; start injecting; vehicular histrionics ensue; stop injecting; car rolls to stop

max_speedometer_attack.description: start from park; drive; accelerate; start injecting; speedometer jumps to maximum, stop injecting; decelerate; park

reverse_light_off_attack.description: start from park; reverse; reverse lights turn on; accelerate; coast; start injecting; reverse lights turn off, stop injecting; reverse lights turn on

reverse_light_on_attack.description: start from park; drive (reverse lights turn on fleetingly when shifting through R); drive; accelerate; start injecting; reverse lights turn on, coast; stop injecting; reverse lights turn off; decelerate; park (reverse lights turn on fleetingly when shifting through R)

correlated_signal_attack.description: start from driving; accelerate; start injecting through end of capture; car rolls to stop

fuzzing_attack.description: start from park; reverse; accelerate; start injecting through end of capture; vehicular histrionics ensue

max_speedometer_attack.description: start from driving; accelerate; start injecting; speedometer jumps to maximum, decelerate, stop injecting; accelerate; decelerate; park

reverse_light_off_attack.description: start from park; reverse; reverse lights turn on; accelerate; coast; start injecting; reverse light turns off, stop injecting; reverse lights turn on

reverse_light_on_attack.description: start from park; drive (reverse lights turn on fleetingly when shifting through R); accelerate; start injecting; reverse lights turn on, accelerate/decelerate/coast; stop injecting; reverse lights turn off; decelerate; park (reverse lights turn on fleetingly when shifting through R)
